# ```
# Classify the following support ticket:
# 
# Few-shot examples:
#   "System down" → Critical/Technical
#   "Refund request" → High/Billing
# 
# Ticket: "{user_input}"
# 
# Classification:
#   Urgency: ___
#   Category: ___
# ```
# 
# Sample user input:
# ```
# I was overcharged $250. I’m on the $49 Pro plan, but got billed $299 for Enterprise. Please refund the difference to my card.
# ```
# 
# Sample LLM Output:
# ```
# {
# "urgency": "high",
# "category": "technical",
